			<h2>The Home Stretch!</h2>
			
			<p>My colleagues and I are doing everything to ensure that Senate DEMOCRATS continue to be a brick wall against Republicans to protect progress we have made. All Virginians deserve well funded schools, affordable healthcare, livable wages, clean air and water, accessible and affordable housing and the freedom to choose their future - whether it's at the ballot box, reproductive healthcare decisions, or keeping our children safe from gun violence.</p>

			<p>Thank you to all the supporters, who have helped me to contribute 1.1 million dollars to the Senate Democratic Caucus and over $150,000 to candidates. BUT WE ARE NOT DONE!
			I need you to continue to invest in strong campaigns, supporting candidates that prioritize the issues that matter to you and me: education, voting rights, abortion rights, healthcare, affordable housing, sensible gun control. I need you to stand with me against extremism and continue to break barriers and build bridges. Your vote is your power to save our democracy!</p>

			<p>Reminder: EARLY voting ends on November 4, 2023. Don't forget to bring your ID to the polls on Election Day, November 7, 2023. The Virginia code 24.2-603 states "the polls shall be open at each polling place at 6:00 a.m. on the day of the election and closed at 7:00 p.m. on the same day except as provided for central absentee voter precincts pursuant to subsection G of ยง 24.2-712. At 6:45 p.m. an officer of election shall announce that the polls will close in fifteen minutes. The officers of election shall list the names of all qualified voters in line before the polling place at 7:00 p.m. and permit those voters and no others to vote after 7:00 p.m."</p>

			<p>If you want to volunteer for our office as a canvasser or poll greeter, please feel free to contact our district office at <a href="tel:757-224-4415">757-224-4415</a> or <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#5f33303c343a39302d2c2b3e2b3a2c3a313e2b3a1f38323e3633713c3032"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="167a79757d73707964656277627365737877627356717b777f7a3875797b">[email&#160;protected]</span></a>. Follow me on Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram. Newsletters will continue to be distributed to keep you informed on happenings in the 23rd District.  Remember, your vote is your voice.</p>

